OL,3,CSix-year-old girl dies after being hit
OL,4,Cby Range Rover
OL,6,FA six-year-old girl has died after
OL,7,Fbeing hit by a Range Rover.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called out to
OL,10,FAshfield Road, in Rochdale, at around
OL,11,F5.35pm on 28 April following reports
OL,12,Fof the incident.
OL,14,FThe Range Rover was travelling
OL,15,Fwestbound when it collided with the
OL,16,Fyoung schoolgirl who had entered the
OL,17,Froad, Greater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,18,Fsaid.
