OL,3,CSix-year-old girl dies after being hit
OL,4,Cby Range Rover
OL,6,FThe girl suffered serious injuries
OL,7,Ffrom the collision and sadly died a
OL,8,Fshort time later. Specialist officers
OL,9,Fare supporting her family.
OL,11,FThe driver remained at the scene and
OL,12,Fno arrests have been made.
OL,14,FOfficers from GMP's Serious Collision
OL,15,FInvestigation Unit (SCIU) are now
OL,16,Finvestigating the incident and their
OL,17,Fenquiries are ongoing.
