OL,6,FThey are appealing for anyone who may
OL,7,Fhave witnessed the incident to come
OL,8,Fforward with any information as soon
OL,9,Fas possible.
OL,11,FDetective Constable Thomas Johnson,
OL,12,Ffrom SCIU, said: "I firstly want to
OL,13,Fpass my condolences onto the family of
OL,14,Fthe girl who tragically died following
OL,15,Flast night's collision.
