OL,6,F"The thoughts of everyone from our
OL,7,Finvestigating team are with them and
OL,8,Fwe are continuing to support them
OL,9,Fwhere we can. As our work progresses,
OL,10,Fwe are asking for anyone with any
OL,11,Finformation to please come forward.
OL,13,F"You may have witnessed last night's
OL,14,Fincident, or have relevant CCTV,
OL,15,Fdoorbell or dashcam footage. If you
OL,16,Fcan send this to our officers, this
OL,17,Fwould be greatly appreciated as we put
OL,18,Ftogether a complete picture of last
OL,19,Fnight's incident."
